name: Vulcain
description: Add a touch of discreet elegance with Vulcain and its sophisticated black metal frame. Its gradient lenses offer sun protection while adding a modern and refined effect to your look.

name: Pandora
description: The Pandora sunglasses, with their rose gold metal frame, bring a touch of timeless elegance. Designed for women, they stand out with their refined style and tinted lenses, perfect for a sophisticated look.

name: Cannes
description: Showcase a glamorous style with the Cannes sunglasses in pearly white acetate and tinted lenses. Perfect for sunny days, they won't go unnoticed!

name: ithasa
description: The Ithasa sunglasses, with their bold and oversized black acetate frame, combine originality and timeless elegance. Designed for women with a bold style, they add a glamorous touch to every look with their tinted lenses.

name: Zadar
description: Choose the Zadar sunglasses, a bold frame in flashy green acetate that makes a style statement. With their tinted lenses, these sunglasses add an original touch to your look, perfect for women who want to stand out.

name: Arezzo
description: Make a statement with Arezzo and its bold bright yellow frame. Its black lenses offer effective sun protection while adding a touch of modernity to your outfits.

name: Valparaiso
description: Adopt the Valparaiso sunglasses, a bold thin red acetate frame that makes a style statement. With their tinted lenses, these sunglasses add an original touch to your look, perfect for women who want to stand out.

name: Jhon
description: The Jhon sunglasses feature a minimalist design with a black acetate frame, combining simplicity and timelessness. Perfect for women seeking a discreet style, they offer elegance and protection with their tinted lenses.

name: Glint
description: Fall for Glint, a translucent green frame that exudes originality and freshness. Its gray lenses provide effective sun protection while enhancing your everyday look.

name: Stellar
description: Brighten up your days with Stellar and its captivating translucent red frame. Its vibrant yellow lenses offer a bright vision while asserting a bold style.

name: Sunrise
description: Add a touch of sophistication with Sunrise and its elegant black frame. Its dark gray lenses ensure optimal sun protection while enhancing your everyday looks.
